Package: ProjectIBR
Title: Qatar Trade & Blockade Panel Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Malek", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "marwan.y.itani@gmail.com")
Description: Reproducible econometric analysis of the 2017 Qatar diplomatic
    crisis on bilateral trade, using a gravity model on a country-year panel.
    Provides functions for data loading, panel construction, stationarity
    testing, fixed/random/pooled/CRE estimation, robust inference, and
    diagnostics. Structured as a project-as-package so logic in R/ is unit
    tested while analysis/ and _targets.R orchestrate the pipeline.
